A 20-year-old woman sits on the sofa wearing a fitted light blue long-sleeved shirt and a beige tight skirt., The image depicts a modern, well-lit living room with a minimalist design. The room features a light-colored beige sofa with a plush, cloud-shaped pillow and a black-and-white cow-print pillow. The sofa is positioned against a wall adorned with three abstract art pieces in wooden frames. The artwork includes various patterns and colors, adding a touch of creativity to the space.

To the left of the sofa, there is a large window with sheer white curtains that allow natural light to filter into the room. A tall, leafy plant in a round white pot sits on a small table beside the window, adding a touch of greenery to the room. The floor is covered with a light-colored area rug that complements the sofa.

The ceiling features recessed lighting, providing ample illumination for the room. There is also a rectangular ceiling air vent, indicating that the room is equipped with modern heating and cooling systems. The overall ambiance of the room is calm and inviting, with a focus on clean lines and a neutral color palette.

A 20-year-old woman sat on the couch wearing a light blue sleeve top and a white tight skirt., The image depicts a cozy and well-decorated living room. The room features a large, light-colored tufted sofa with several cushions, including one with the text "I ❤️ ❤️" and another with a floral pattern. In front of the sofa, there is a round wooden coffee table with a vase of yellow flowers and a couple of books. The floor is covered with a light-colored rug.

To the left of the sofa, there is a wooden side table with a lamp and a few decorative items, including a small sculpture and a plant. Behind the sofa, there is a wall painted in a soft green color, adorned with a large painting of a floral arrangement.

In the background, there is an open kitchen area with white cabinetry and a view of some kitchen appliances. There is also a wicker chair with a floral cushion and a small table next to it. The ceiling features a modern chandelier with multiple spherical lights.

The overall ambiance of the room is warm and inviting, with a mix of modern and vintage elements.

 第二步：填写提示词。

 第三步：点击生成。

 第四步：保存结果图，并上传到下面的高清放大组件，最后点击生成。
